flavor wheel that I had gotten from a barrel

00:40:37.499 --> 00:40:41.400
manufacturer that showed all these different
flavors you get from oak, and one of them

00:40:41.400 --> 00:40:46.699
is like an herbaceous dill character.
So that's something you get out of the oak

00:40:46.699 --> 00:40:50.059
for this particular beer.
And interestingly enough, I mentioned, if

00:40:50.059 --> 00:40:54.710
