of the oak.

00:41:07.401 --> 00:41:11.489
Or at least the flavors that come out of the
oak express themselves differently in each

00:41:11.489 --> 00:41:15.539
of these different kinds of beers.
So it's really interesting.

00:41:15.539 --> 00:41:17.650
The Curieux -- you get that dill from the
oak.

00:41:17.650 --> 00:41:21.140
We do another beer called the 'Musette' that's
